      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "requiredLevel": 4,
      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Primary QoI (hemolysis index) directly maps to clinical endpoint; secondary QoIs (wall shear stress, scalar transport) documented.",
      "rationale": "Hemolysis index is clinically relevant; however, platelet activation index—a secondary QoI of regulatory interest—is not extracted from the simulation outputs."
